# This repository tracks only Android, Kotlin, and KMP-related skills.
#
# Strategy: ignore every entry at the repo root by default, then re-include
# the specific skill families (and a few individually named skills) that
# belong here. Anything not matched below stays out of this repo.

# Ignore everything at the root by default.
/*

# Keep repo metadata.
!.gitignore
!README.md
!LICENSE

# Skill families kept in this repo.
!android-*/
!kotlin-*/
!agent-*/
!kmp-*/
!architecture-*/
!handoff/
!git-*/
!figma-*/
!speckit-*/

# Individual Android/Compose skills that fall outside the prefixes above.
!compose-adaptive-layouts/

# Never track macOS Finder cruft, even inside kept skills.
**/.DS_Store
